
"Cavalcade O' Card Games"  (v2.5s) was designed for shareware users to
register and then receive an updated version containing all nine games
shown in the shareware version.  The shareware version is meant to be
registered if it is continued to be used past a reasonable trial period.
Free distribution of this shareware game is encouraged so far as the
conditions as stated below are followed.  Commercial distribution is also
discussed below.  The rest of this document will be referring only to 
Cavalcade O' Card Games shareware, version 2.5s, unless otherwise noted.

GENERAL CONDITIONS FOR DISTRIBUTION:

When distributed by any means Cavalcade O' Card Games must be distributed
with all the following files intact and unaltered:

	CAVAL25S.EXE      DATA2.CGS
	SOURCE1.DAT       DATA4.CGS
	SOURCE2.DAT       DATA5.CGS
	SOURCE3.DAT       INSTRUCT.TEX
	SOURCE4.DAT       
	SOURCE5.DAT       VENDOR.DOC
	SOURCE6.DAT       FILE_ID.DIZ
	SOURCE7.DAT
	DATA1.CGS


If this program is condensed, compressed or archived please use the 
name caval25s.* .

Under no circumstances is the full nine game registered version of
Cavalcade O' Card Games to be distributed without the prior consent
of the author, Derek Duban.



FOR SHAREWARE DISTRIBUTORS:

- If you are interested in distributing this product please follow the 
conditions stated above and fill in the questionnaire at the end of this 
document.
- We would appreciate notification if you choose to distribute this 
shareware product.  
- If you issue a catalogue please send us a copy with our product in it.  
- Any information about this product can be sent to you upon request.
- If you take registrations on behalf of authors and are interested in 
picking up this game please contact the address below.

ORDERS AND COMMUNICATIONS:

